name: Copy of منصة امتحانات هندسة المعلوماتية الموحدة
description: A comprehensive platform for managing and taking informational engineering exams, with standard and AI-generated question capabilities. The application supports both students and administrators, offering features like exam setup, AI-powered question generation, exam sessions with timers, and results review. It is styled using Tailwind CSS and built with React and TypeScript.
